# Layer5 — Production Build Plan
### Phase 0 Artifact | CONFIDENTIAL | v1.0 — March 2026

> **Status**: AWAITING REVIEW — No code has been written. Each phase begins only after you type `APPROVED — BEGIN PHASE [N]`.

---

## Project Overview

Layer5 is a 6-layer, append-only, outcome-ranked decision intelligence middleware that sits between any LLM and enterprise infrastructure. The architecture is a PostgreSQL star schema (Supabase) + Node.js REST API + Edge Functions + lightweight dashboard.

---

## Project Structure

```
