## Approval Protocol

After reviewing this document:

1. Leave comments on any section you want revised — I will update the plan
2. When you are satisfied with a phase, type exactly: `APPROVED — BEGIN PHASE [N]`
3. I will build **only** that phase — no adjacent code will be written
4. After building, I will run the test gate and show you results
5. Only when you type `APPROVED — BEGIN PHASE [N+1]` will the next phase begin

> [!IMPORTANT]
> No code will be written until you type the explicit approval command for a specific phase. The plan above is the complete contract for what will be built.
